{"type": "article", "id": 24302, "title": "鸡尾酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-23T07:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121011w3Op6ykuDBY7cHlx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这瓶酒的包装令人想起汽水，包装上不同颜色之间的边缘就像被浪花冲刷的海滩。红色和蓝色是极具张力的对比色，上面用银色泊纸写下了 Seaworthy 和几行诗句，在活泼中带点清新。Seaworthy 原本指能够海运，这几个字的光泽也有点像海滩上的珍珠。然而这款略显清新的包装却是放血腥玛丽这样重口味的鸡尾酒。插画设计来自澳大利亚 Webuyyourkids，<a href=\"http://squadink.com/#/project/seaworthy-vodka/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121008Fyuk8H15aAYK7mPC.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.94375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121009XRAQg3EvziDxSCZj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6802974\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121010pmgfy1PvEBcxdb3F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71003717\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121010Fwy96bCKIa2fEWzM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97583643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121011FG1ZmVLQUMcru8WR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2936803\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}